or: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Edit view for consents includes</span></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>UUID</li>\r\n<li>CCUUID</li>\r\n<li><span id="docs-internal-guid-c0653b2a-7fff-501a-c71e-f78e9a6caeb1"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Consent Opt-in</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span id="docs-internal-guid-c0653b2a-7fff-501a-c71e-f78e9a6caeb1"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Consent Opt-out</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span id="docs-internal-guid-72324b4d-7fff-7f45-b46a-34fac67a06ce"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Consent Date</span></span></li>\r\n<li>URL</li>\r\n<li><span id="docs-internal-guid-a92153f2-7fff-1262-d030-18e331af4d5f"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">User Agent of the browser</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Pull Request -</strong>&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><a href="https://github.com/joomla-projects/gsoc21_cookie-manager/pull/10">https://github.com/joomla-projects/gsoc21_cookie-manager/pull/10</a><a href="https://github.com/joomla-project