	(1642, 0, 78, 'Certification Program: update September 2021', 'certification-program-update-september-2021', '<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;">In September the JCP team held 2 short meetings to discuss various tasks and progress.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;">Participants:</h3>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><em>Attendees:</em><span style="caret-color: auto;"></span><span style="caret-color: auto;">Chris Keen (TL),&nbsp;</span><span style="caret-color: auto;">Jeroen Moolenschot</span></p>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><em>Absent with apologies:&nbsp;</em><span style="caret-color: auto;">Luca Marzo<br /><em>Guest:</em>&nbsp;Jaz Parkyn (Dept. Co-ordinator) - not present<br /></span></p>\r\n<h2 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;">General points</h2>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">None</span></p>\r\n<h3 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><span style="text-decoration-line: underline;"><strong>Team news</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">We are still urgently seeking&nbsp;</span><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">to recruit two new team members, an&nbsp;<strong>Operations and Marketing Coordinator</strong>&nbsp;and a&nbsp;<strong>Platform Developer</strong>.<br />These positions were posted in the May issue of the Joomla Community Magazine (JCM), community openings article:-<br /><a href="https://magazine.joomla.org/all-issues/may-2021/community-openings-may-2021">https://magazine.joomla.org/all-issues/may-2021/community-openings-may-2021</a>&nbsp;<br />So far we have not received any reactions.&nbsp;If you\'re interested or know someone suitable please contact us (or me directly).</span></p>\r\n<h2 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;">Operations and Marketing</h2>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;">There are no other updates from the Operations and Marketing team (mainly due to the lack of exams).</p>\r\n<h2 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">Website and Exam platform</span></h2>\r\n<h3 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><strong>Shika: (new exam platform) - no change since June.</strong></h3>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><em>At this point in time we have not found any \'show stoppers\' with Shika itself, but have some problems with the question management component. We need a Platform Developer to help us with this, as mentioned above, the position has been shared in the May issue of the JCM (see above).</em></p>\r\n<h2 style="font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3">Exam(s)</span></h2>\r\n<h3 style="font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; color: #333333; overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: auto;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-db13cfb0-7fff-1e7f-2d9c-50751520fef3" style="color: #333333; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></span></span>J!4 Administrator exam (and no update to the J!3 version)</h3>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: auto;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-fa6f5df6-7fff-6772-8e79-e390e9ee64f5" style="color: #333333; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br />We have upgraded the Question Management System (QMS) to J!4. We are now implemented the workflow features in J!4 tand are testing and refining the process.<br /><br />We are planning a meeting with our Exam Maintainers to test and verify this process and workflow. Once finalised we can the start with updating the J!3 Administrator exam to J!4.<br /><br /><em><span style="font-size: 14.6667px;">(In July the JCP team and the Programs Department members agreed to us focussing on updating the Administration Exam to reflect the forthcoming release of Joomla version 4.0. It was always agreed that we will not update the J!3 version of the Administrator exam.)</span></em><br /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<h2 style="font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; color: #333333; overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: auto;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-fa6f5df6-7fff-6772-8e79-e390e9ee64f5" style="color: #333333; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span style="text-decoration-line: underline;">Upcoming Meeting(s):</span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: auto;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-fa6f5df6-7fff-6772-8e79-e390e9ee64f5" style="color: #333333; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><strong style="color: #333333; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;">JCP monthly team meeting:&nbsp;</strong><span style="color: #333333; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;">13th October 2021.</span><span style="caret-color: auto;"></span><br /></span></span></span><strong>Project / isssue progress meeting:&nbsp;</strong><span style="caret-color: auto;">27th October</span><span style="caret-color: auto;">&nbsp;2021</span></p>', NULL, 1, 1328, 1, 1093, '2021-10-04 19:01:12', 0, '2021-10-04 19:08:32', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1643, 56, 0, 'Programs Department Meeting - 5th October 2021 ', 'programs-department-meeting-5th-october-2021', '<p>Participants: Jaz Parkyn, Chris Keen, Patrick Jackson, Wilco Alsemgeest</p>\r\n<p>Dept:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Semi-annual meeting is upcoming, please review the agenda and add any questions you may have.</li>\r\n<li>To review ahead of the meeting: <a href="https://github.com/open-source-matters/contact-us/discussions/3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">A lighter structure of Open Source Matters, Inc.</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>JCP:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Update JVP report for September: <a href="teams/certification-team/reports/1642-certification-program-update-september-2021">https://volunteers.joomla.org/teams/certification-team/reports/1642-certification-program-update-september-2021</a></li>\r\n<li>THe Q&amp;A review process has been designed and implemented through the workflow functionality (including all necessary stages and transitions).</li>\r\n<li>The original custom fields are being reviewed and adjusted as necessary (many now unnecessary due to the implementation of the workflow).&nbsp; New custom fields have been added to match the proposed workflow.<br />The front-end (template) has been modified to show many of the necessary fields and functions to make this process easier (still a few missing information fields). Thanks to Jeroen</li>\r\n<li>Test and review session with the Exam Maintainers (EM’s) is being planned. (The EM’s will work from out the front-end).</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>VET:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Holding off on meeting to be able to best digest the restructure proposal.</li>\r\n<li>Next meeting scheduled October 18 2021 at 20:00 UTC</li>\r\n<li>Robert Deutz will be joining the October meeting to discuss where he sees VET fitting into his agenda.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>JTP:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Production department is going to migrate JoomlaCode on October 16, 2021 to the <a href="https://downloads.joomla.org">https://downloads.joomla.org</a> website.</li>\r\n<li>Docs pages revamped or created:<br /><a href="https://docs.joomla.org/Special:MyLanguage/Joomla_Translation_Program">https://docs.joomla.org/Special:MyLanguage/Joomla_Translation_Program</a> <br /><a href="https://docs.joomla.org/Crowdin">https://docs.joomla.org/Crowdin</a>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>To be done:<br /><a href="https://docs.joomla.org/JDOC:Crowdin_for_Proofreaders">https://docs.joomla.org/JDOC:Crowdin_for_Proofreaders</a> <br /><a href="https://docs.joomla.org/Special:MyLanguage/Joomla_Project_Translations">https://docs.joomla.org/Special:MyLanguage/Joomla_Project_Translations</a>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>New Language coordinators in September<br />Afrikaans, Czech, Estonian and Finnish<br /><a href="teams/joomla-cms-language-team">https://volunteers.joomla.org/teams/joomla-cms-language-team</a>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 1329, 2, 695, '2021-10-05 20:23:59', 695, '2021-10-05 20:40:11', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1644, 0, 51, 'CMS Release Team Meeting Oct 6, 2021', 'cms-release-team-meeting-oct-6-2021', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-8382c7e5-7fff-578c-71d4-e2fda4d6d088" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Wed, Oct 06, 2021, UTC 18:00</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">DETAILS</span><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Duration: 60&nbsp; Minutes</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Participants:</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Jenn, Benjamin, Claudia, Sigrid, Rachel, Harald, Phil</span></p>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">AGENDA</span></h2>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">1. Automated Testing</span></h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We had a workshop on October 1st about Automated Testing. We looked into iMacro, Selenium, Codeception. There is a lot of documentation on JDocs about Codeception testing. We will check if the documentation is still working and how we could simplify it for more people.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">One part is to support automated testing for Joomla in general, the other part is testing in local environments for RCs to support our team members. As Codeception is PHP based this would be the closest to our work.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">2. Release Check Sheet</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Claudia added the new J4 functions to our Release Check list - thanks a lot so far! When we test the next release we will continue to add the tasks to the missing component areas. This checksheet will also be the basis for the automated tests.</span></p>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">3. RCR Process</span></h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Testing checklist is linked from JDocs</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Pre Release Testing JDoc → Links to checksheet</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">“Low-Level” meeting for testing → make a concept for testing - easy access</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Marketing Liaison to get people motivated</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">JUG Lists</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">→ invite people from “important” Joomla community members</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Easy checklist - one channel different rooms</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Monday Oct 16th UTC 17:00</span></p>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">4. Documentation Session</span></h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Phil and Sigrid had a tutorial session with Mike about JDocs. Unfortunately it was not recorded, Mike offered to re-record for us.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Next CMS Release team meeting is scheduled for Wed. Oct. 27, 18:00 UTC</span></p>', NULL, 1, 1330, 1, 1036, '2021-10-08 18:42:22', 0, '2021-10-08 18:43:24', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1645, 0, 25, 'Joomla Bug Squad Meeting - October 8, 2021', 'joomla-bug-squad-meeting-october-8-2021', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-a8b3a6e6-7fff-d136-a816-714c0fc7616f" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Date:</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> October 8, 2021</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Time:</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> 18:00 CEST</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.9871999999999999; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Total time of meeting:</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color