lease candidates should be the same as the final release. If RC changes → new RC</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">If there are changes after RC → the release leads will post information to glip team channel for extra testing.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The process has to be realistic.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Sigrid will talk to release leads.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">2. What needs to be changed or added in the migration docs for the .htaccess stuff for 4.0.5</span></h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">There will be one line in the docs. Jenn will post to glip channel.</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Phil created an FAQ - </span><a href="https://docs.joomla.org/Htaccess_changes_after_joomla4.0.4" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">https://docs.joomla.org/Htaccess_changes_after_joomla4.0.4</span></a><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></p>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">3. Splitting up/focusing on testing 3.10.x and 4.x</span></h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Both should be tested equally, but also depending on the number of changes. If there are only a few changes in 3, then more testing in 4.</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We will keep communication in Glip channel - who is doing what - Joomla and PHP versions</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">4. Status 4.1</span></h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Benjamin introduced the new planned features for 4.1 to us:</span></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Scheduler (GSoC) - in Alpha3 End of Nov. (feature freeze)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Accessibility Checker for authors</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Statistic plugin - optimize</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Child templates</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Tiny MCE - Code highlighting, Language code</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/releases/tag/4.1.0-alpha2</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Next CMS Release team meeting is scheduled for Wed. Nov. 17, 18:00 UTC</span></p>', NULL, 1, 1350, 1, 1036, '2021-11-27 16:07:13', 0, '2021-11-27 16:08:22', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1665, 54, 0, '13th November, 2021 Events Department Meeting', '13th-november-2021-events-department-meeting', '<p><span id="docs-internal-guid-777e0af1-7fff-11b3-8ff5-8adf0378ff05"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; color: #000000; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Scheduled length of time</span><span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; color: #000000; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">: 1 hour</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Participants:</span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> David Aswani (Department) </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Shirielle (SD) Williams (Events) Patrick Jackson (PBF) Todd Woodward (JUG)</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Agenda:</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Department:</strong></p>\r\n<p><span id="docs-internal-guid-60b8cef9-7fff-3ce5-ec36-2e9a1bf107d6"></span></p>\r\n<ol style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Did an interview with the JCM Team to be published soon.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The motion of Lighter OSM structure and by-laws amendment passed at the board. (the </span><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\',sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">document has been updated to reflect the proposal discussed during the last Board Meeting).</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Events Team:</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Sobipro to DPCalendar:- </span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The migration is in progress on the live site. Need to follow up with Wilco on when the menu items will change. The DPCalendar configurations are in place behind the scenes.&nbsp; A new permission group has been created DPCalendar Admin.</span></p>\r\n<p>Event Process/Procedures:- SD and Phil, have discussed how things are changing. A draft will be created in the next few weeks.</p>\r\n<p><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Newsletter:- </span>Discussed with Phil/Marketing DC about automating a newsletter for events. The DPCalendar plugin can be activated.</p>\r\n<p><strong>JUG Team:</strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-27d5a1cb-7fff-6d39-fe9a-453013a0311c"></span></span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The team is conducting outreach to known JUG leader/organizer contacts. Meetings are to be held Thursday, November 11, and today. Patrick attended the Thursday meeting. Shout out to Laura Gordon for moving the ball forward.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>PBF Team:</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Looking to schedule a meeting to plan the new format of PBF / Joomla Internal events going forward.</span></p>\r\n<p><b id="docs-internal-guid-55e31cbe-7fff-b326-3539-88ee06aabf46" style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</b></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Options:</span></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Continue with a single weekend PBF</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Expand to a month-long Joomla Hackathon potentially twice a year.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">One early 2022</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The second one October coincides with Digital Ocean Hacktoberfest, which then comes with an existing community, discord server, and onboarding opportunities.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Additionally this working group may pivot to assist VET with running onboarding events, as well as being a group that runs internal Joomla events (becoming a virtual pseudo-JUG).</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></p>', NULL, 1, 1351, 1, 901, '2021-12-01 10:58:44', 0, '2021-12-01 11:09:14', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1666, 0, 51, 'CMS Release Team Meeting Nov 17, 2021', 'cms-release-team-meeting-nov-17-2021', '<p id="docs-internal-guid-53f69db5-7fff-1457-ce46-9df1401f8b4a" dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Wed, Nov 17, 2021, UTC 18:00</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">DETAILS</span><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Duration:&nbsp; 60 Minutes</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 14pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Participants:</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Phil, B