lor: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Scheduler (GSoC) - in Alpha3 End of Nov. (feature freeze) - this weekend</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">More information/documentation</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Accessibility Checker for authors (2 weeks)</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;" aria-level="1">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: #16181d; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-d