lection Results</span></h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Jacob Waisner has been elected as the new team lead. 14 team members were eligible to vote, 12 have voted, 2 haven’t attended. Jacob was the only candidate. From the 12 voters, 8 have voted for Jacob, which are 66.67% of the voters and 57.14% of the members.</span></p>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Next Meeting</span></h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The next team meeting will be: Fri, June 3 at 6:00 PM CEST (4:00 PM UTC)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 1425, 1, 1053, '2022-06-02 21:20:31', 0, '2022-06-02 21:21:09', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
