	(1768, 0, 175, 'GSoC 2022 : A11y-Plugin - Week 1', 'gsoc-2022-a11y-plugin-week-1', '<h1 dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 20pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Discussions Done in the week:</span></strong></h1>\r\n<ul style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Had first meeting with my mentors.</span></span></li>\r\n<li>Discussed about the flow of the project.</li>\r\n<li>Mentors told me about the external library which joomla uses for a11y plugin.</li>\r\n<li>Discussed about the set up of the project repo.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Tasks completed in the week:</span></strong></h2>\r\n<ul style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li>Done with setting up the external library locally.</li>\r\n<li>Refactored the code of accessibility.php to support change position feature.</li>\r\n<li>Implemented the Change Position feature for a11y icon from the site backend.</li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #121212; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Prioritized the tasks for next week.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 1454, 3, 7208, '2022-06-19 07:26:14', 7208, '2022-07-15 08:34:26', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1769, 0, 175, 'GSoC 2022 : A11y_Plugin - Week 2', 'gsoc-2022-a11y-plugin-week-2', '<h2 dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Tasks completed in the week:</span></strong></h2>\r\n<ul style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li><span style="color: #121212; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Spent time on understanding the code base of the external a11y libray to learn how it alters properties like Text Size, Word Spacing, etc.</span></li>\r\n<li>Understood the how the session persistence being maintained using cache.</li>\r\n<li>Implemented the Increase/Decrease Line Height Feature</li>\r\n<li>Exteneded the reset functionality for Line Height.</li>\r\n<li>Maintained session persistence for line height.</li>\r\n<li>Made line height work for textEml mode and textPixel mode.</li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #121212; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14.6667px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Prioritized the task for next week.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="overflow-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Git Branch :&nbsp;</strong><a href="https://github.com/joomla-projects/gsoc22_accessibility-plugin-script/tree/lineHeight"><span style="caret-color: auto;">https://github.com/joomla-projects/gsoc22_accessibility-plugin-script/tree/lineHeight</span></a></p>', NULL, 1, 1455, 1, 7208, '2022-06-26 08:15:05', 0, '2022-07-15 08:32:32', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1770, 0, 175, 'GSoC 2022 : A11y-Plugin - Week 3', 'gsoc-2022-a11y-plugin-week-3', '<h2 dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Tasks completed in the week:</span></strong></h2>\r\n<ul style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li>Started the week by reading the documentation of speechSynthesis Web API.</li>\r\n<li>Spent time on understanding the existing implementation of text to speech in the a11y external script.</li>\r\n<li>Developed the initial design of speech velocity feature.</li>\r\n<li>Implemeted the speech velocity so that the user can choose the desired the reading velocity from : Normal, fast and slow.</li>\r\n<li>Tested the speech velocity for cross browser compatibility.</li>\r\n<li>Improved the announcements made by other functions of a11y plugin when Screen Reader is enabled.</li>\r\n<li>Spent time in figuring out the reason of a major bug in the a11y plugin, i.e., sometimes screen reader starts reading, and doesn\'t stops till the tab is closed.</li>\r\n<li>Prioritized the task for next week.<br /><br /><strong>Git branch</strong> :&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/joomla-projects/gsoc22_accessibility-plugin-script/tree/speechVelocity">https://github.com/joomla-projects/gsoc22_accessibility-plugin-script/tree/speechVelocity</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 1456, 2, 7208, '2022-07-03 08:35:32', 7208, '2022-07-15 09:13:51', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1771, 0, 175, 'GSoC 2022 : A11y-Plugin - Week 4', 'gsoc-2022-a11y-plugin-week-4', '<h2 dir="ltr" style="margin-top: 18pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; line-height: 1.38; color: #333333;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Tasks completed in the week:</span></strong></h2>\r\n<ul style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li>Started the week by reading about the importance of Dyslexic Font.</li>\r\n<li>Implemented the open dyslexic font feature in the a11y panel.</li>\r\n<li>Selected \'OpenDyslexic\' font to be used as the dyslexic font in the a11y plugin.</li>\r\n<li>Downloaded the different variants( OpenDyslexic monochrome &amp; OpenDyslexic Regular) from the Github repo of OpenDyslexic.</li>\r\n<li>Integrated the fonts with the a11y external script.</li>\r\n<li>Wrote CSS to enhance the open dyslexic font.</li>\r\n<li>Updated the reading velocity feature so that the announcements are made for open dyslexic font feature, Increase/decrease text size feature, Increase/decrease line height feature.</li>\r\n<li>Prioritized the tasks for the upcoming week.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style="margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;">\r\n<li><strong>Git branch:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><a href="https://github.com/joomla-projects/gsoc22_accessibility-plugin-script/tree/dyslexicFont">https://github.com/joomla-projects/gsoc22_accessibility-plugin-script/tree/dyslexicFont</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 1457, 5, 7208, '2022-07-10 09:14:25', 7208, '2022-07-15 09:42:45', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1772, 0, 177, 'GSoC 2022 – Schema.org | Week 5', 'gsoc-2022-schema-org-week-5', '<p><strong>Date:</strong> 11th July – 15th July</p>\r\n<p>Hi, this is the progress report for the Schema.org project which is currently part of GSoC 2022.</p>\r\n<p>Tasks completed this week:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Updated manifest files</li>\r\n<li>Created onSchemaPrepareForm event in plg_schemaorg_recipe plugin to add a new option in schema type list field in schema form</li>\r\n<li>Dispatched onSchemaPrepareForm event in plg_system_schema plugin</li>\r\n<li>Created xml form for Recipe schema type</li>\r\n<li>Used subform to display form fields of selected schema type&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 1458, 1, 7190, '2022-07-16 05:40:22', 0, '2022-07-16 05:42:45', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(1773, 51, 0, 'Production Dept. Meeting MINUTES - July 12, 2022', 'production-dept-meeting-minutes-july-12-2022', '<h1 style="text-align: right;">Production Dept. Meeting MINUTES <br />- July&nbsp; 12, 2022</h1>\r\n<p><strong>Participants:</strong> Benjamin Trenkle (Department Coordinator), David Jardin (Team Leader), , Harald Leithner (Release Lead 5.0), Mike Brandner (Team Leader), Franciska Perisa (Release Lead 4.2), Christiane Maier-Stadtherr (Team Leader), Niels Braczek (Team Leader), Llewellyn van der Merwe (Assistant Department Coordinator), Sigrid Gramlinger (Team Leader), Shivam Rajput (Team Leader), Philip Walton (Marketing Liaison), Tobias Zulauf (Release Lead 3.10) <br /> <strong>Absent:</strong> Viviana Menzel (Assistant Team Leader), Hannes Papenberg (Team Leader), Jacob Waisner (Team Leader), Robert Deutz (Team Leader), Roland Dalmulder (Release Lead 4.2)</p>\r\n<h3><a href="/departments/production">Production Department</a> Coordinator (Benjamin Trenkle)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Motion: Rename Release Lead to Release Manager starting with Joomla! 4.3</li>\r\n<li>Motion: Elect Olivier Buisard and Shirielle Williams as Joomla! 4.3 Release Manager</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>Joomla! <a href="/teams/accessibility-team">Accessibility</a> Team (Christiane Maier-Stadtherr)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We are preparing some ideas for a11y documentation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><a href="/teams/automated-tests-working-group">Automated Testing</a> Team (Hannes Papenberg)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Cypress works now in the CI, now the testing framework (Common tasks like login) are missing. And of course tests.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>Releaseleads (Harald, Niels, Roland, Franciska, Benjamin, George, Tobias, Llewellyn)</h3>\r\n<h4>* Release Lead 5.0 (Harald Leithner, Niels Braczek):</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Motion set minimum supported [<a href="https://downloads.joomla.org/technical-requirements#footnote-minimum">7</a>] PHP version to 8.1.0\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>8.0 will be EOL couple of month after planned release</li>\r\n<li>8.1 supports fibers which we would like to to support at this point in time</li>\r\n<li>Earlier versions may work but are not guaranteed to work (see footnote 7 on technical requirements page)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Motion set minimum supported [<a href="https://downloads.joomla.org/technical-requirements#footnote-minimum">7</a>] MySQL version to 8.0.11\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>8.0.11 is the first stable release for 8 series</li>\r\n<li>5.7 will be EOL couple of month after planned release</li>\r\n<li>Earlier versions may work but are not guaranteed to work (see footnote 7 on technical requirements page)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Motion set minimum supported [<a href="https://downloads.joomla.org/technical-requirements#footnote-minimum">7</a>] MariaDB version to 10.4.0\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>10.3 will be EOL couple of month before planned release</li>\r\n<li>Earlier versions may work but are not guaranteed to work (see footnote 7 on technical requirements page)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Motion set minimum supported [<a href="https://downloads.joomla.org/technical-requirements#footnote-minimum">7</a>] Postgresql version to 12.0\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>11.3 will be EOL couple of month after planned release</li>\r\n<li>Earlier versions may work but are not guaranteed to work (see footnote 7 on technical requirements page)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Motion set minimum supported [<a href="https://downloads.joomla.org/technical-requirements#footnote-minimum">7</a>] nginx version to 1.21\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>1.20 is already EOL</li>\r\n<li>Earlier versions may work but are not guaranteed to work (see footnote 7 on technical requirements page)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Roadmap document in progress thanks to Benjamin</li>\r\n<li>Pull request with initial version requirements created (needs some work)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>* Release Lead 4.2 (Roland Dalmulder, Franciska Perisa)</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>We will build the Release Candidate on saturday to release it on the 19th</li>\r\n<li>RC1 brings language freeze</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>* Maintainer Framework (Niels Braczek):</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Preparing v3, expected to be available in a week or so.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3><a href="/teams/documentation-team">Documentation</a> Team (Mike Brandner)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dropping the programmers documentation try and preparing a Docusaurus documentation for programmers/accessibility/seo/… before the documentation sprint</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>Other Business</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Internal documentation needs now authentication thru identity.joomla.org</li>\r\n<li>Internal documentation has been converted from mkdocs to docusaurus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 1459, 3, 1755, '2022-07-18 10:27:56', 1755, '2022-07-18 10:36:54', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
